lo but I always have the most fun in group and I think this would seriously add to our class.<br><br>This and the lowering of the mana cost of the group taps to lower than the SK taps would be sweet.<br><br>Hey McWorld it can happen<br><br>Aiaka Masaki<br>lvl 47 Necromancer<br>&quot;41 days till i can again bring evil into the world&quot;<br>Wild Hunt of Zeb, Pround member of the Burning Flame Alliance <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/umordeithbonewalker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mordeith Bonewalker</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_ball.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 96<br> <font color=#333333>(4/1/02 10:32:28 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub41.ezboard.com/fthecrossroadstavern8833frm21.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=85.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://ldnews.kyid.net/images/members/mordieth.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Lots of crap from EQNecro but one gem hidden in there</span><hr size=1> Personally I do not think thats a good idea to give us a group haste.  If it is anything at all like our current group buffs  they would only last for 1 min and 30 seconds.   I personally do not want to be recasting my melee group buffs over and over again and loose the fun of my class.  <br><br>I mean if you thought twitching clerics were boring, how about recasting haste for tanks!  Not a good idea. <p><IMG SRC=http://ldnews.kyid.net/images/members/mordieth.jpg><BR><bold>Mordieth Bonewalker</bold><italic> 60 Warlock</italic><BR><bold>Belsamber </bold><italic> 52 Wanderer</italic><BR><bold>Zedikai</bold><italic> 47 Monk</italic><BR><bold>Minimordy</bold><italic> 13 gnome warrior of DEWM!</italic><BR><bold><italic>Residents of Zeboxoruk</bold></italic><B